Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, see you tomorrow.}Uh, gặp cậu vào ngày mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hello}Chào em, Mitsuki-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hi.}Xin chào.
